# Week 1 — ML Foundations Assignment

This repository contains my Week 1 assignment completed during the Data Science Internship at Celebal Technologies.

## Topics Covered
- Python Fundamentals
- NumPy
- Pandas
- Linear Algebra
- Statistics
- Probability Theory

## Concepts Implemented
- Data Types and Control Flow
- Functions and Exception Handling
- Array Operations and Matrix Computations
- Data Analysis using Pandas
- Eigenvalues, Eigenvectors and SVD
- Descriptive and Inferential Statistics
- Hypothesis Testing
- Error Metrics
- Distribution and Stationarity Testing
- Population Stability Index (PSI)
- Probability and Bayes' Theorem
- Central Limit Theorem (CLT)

